{"id": "26842", "post": "<div class=\"post-26842 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-editorial tag-breach tag-digitalocean tag-docn tag-hacked tag-security\" id=\"post-26842\"><h2 class=\"storytitle\"><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/digitalocean-customer-billing-data-exposed-in-security-breach/\" rel=\"bookmark\">DigitalOcean Customer Billing Data Exposed in Security Breach</a></h2><div class=\"meta\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" data-src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" alt=\"Tags: \" class=\"litespeed-loaded\" data-was-processed=\"true\"> <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/breach/\" rel=\"tag\">breach</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/digitalocean/\" rel=\"tag\">digitalocean</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/docn/\" rel=\"tag\">docn</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/hacked/\" rel=\"tag\">Hacked</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/security/\" rel=\"tag\">Security</a> <img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" alt=\"Date/Time: \" class=\"litespeed-loaded\" data-was-processed=\"true\"> April 28, 2021 @ 5:46 pm, by raindog308</div><div class=\"storycontent tablelook\"><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2199/02/digitalocean_300.png.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-26476 litespeed-loaded\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2199/02/digitalocean_300.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" align=\"right\" hspace=\"20\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2199/02/digitalocean_300.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2199/02/digitalocean_300-150x150.png.webp 150w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2199/02/digitalocean_300.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2199/02/digitalocean_300-150x150.png.webp 150w\" data-was-processed=\"true\"><a href=\"https://www.digitalocean.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">DigitalOcean</a> (<a href=\"https://www.marketwatch.com/investing/stock/DOCN?mod=MW_story_quote\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">DOCN</a>) acknowledged today that it has informed some customers that DO had \u201cconfirmed an unauthorized exposure of details associated with the billing profile on your DigitalOcean account.\u201d&nbsp; The breach apparently affected <a href=\"https://www.zdnet.com/article/digital-ocean-says-it-exposed-customer-data-after-it-left-an-internal-doc-online/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">less than 1%</a> of the company\u2019s users.</p><p>DO has since fixed the security flaw that lead to this <a href=\"https://techcrunch.com/2021/04/28/digitalocean-customer-billing-data-breach/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">unauthorized access</a>, which happened between April 9 and April 22.&nbsp; A copy of the email to customers is <a href=\"https://twitter.com/lucaslealdev/status/1258844411347288075/photo/1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">available on Twitter</a>.</p><p>The information leaked includes</p><ul><li>Billing names</li><li>Billing addresses</li><li>Last four of payment card</li><li>Payment card expiry date</li><li>Name of the issuing back</li><li>Number of servers (droplets in DO parlance) the customer uses</li><li>User\u2019s bandwidth usage</li><li>Support notes</li><li>Total invoices for 2018</li></ul><p>Passwords and access credentials were not leaked.</p><p>The root cause was an internal document which was accidentally made available online.</p><p>DigitalOcean went public in March 2021.</p><div class=\"relpost-thumb-wrapper\"><div class=\"relpost-thumb-container\"><h3>Related posts:</h3><div style=\"clear: both\"></div><div style=\"clear: both\"></div><div class=\"relpost-block-container\"><a class=\"relpost-block-single\" href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/a-group-of-friends-making-one-of-the-worlds-most-popular-panels-interview-with-directadmins-co-owner-martynas-bendorius/\"><div class=\"relpost-custom-block-single\" style=\"width: 150px; height: 215px;\"><div class=\"relpost-block-single-image\" alt=\"A Group of Friends Making One of the World's Most Popular Panels: Interview with DirectAdmin's Co-Ow...\" style=\"background: transparent url(https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/da_interview_pic-150x150.jpg) no-repeat scroll 0% 0%; width: 150px; height: 150px;\"></div><div class=\"relpost-block-single-text\" style=\"font-family: Arial;  font-size: 12px;  color: #333333;\">A Group of Friends Making One of the World's Most Popular Panels: Interview with DirectAdmin's Co-Ow...</div></div></a><a class=\"relpost-block-single\" href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/automating-mysql_secure_installation-in-mariadb-setup/\"><div class=\"relpost-custom-block-single\" style=\"width: 150px; height: 215px;\"><div class=\"relpost-block-single-image\" alt=\"Automating mysql_secure_installation in MariaDB Setup\" style=\"background: transparent url(https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/leb-centered-small.jpg) no-repeat scroll 0% 0%; width: 150px; height: 150px;\"></div><div class=\"relpost-block-single-text\" style=\"font-family: Arial;  font-size: 12px;  color: #333333;\">Automating mysql_secure_installation in MariaDB Setup</div></div></a><a class=\"relpost-block-single\" href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/running-your-own-openvpn-vpn-server/\"><div class=\"relpost-custom-block-single\" style=\"width: 150px; height: 215px;\"><div class=\"relpost-block-single-image\" alt=\"Running Your Own OpenVPN VPN Server\" style=\"background: transparent url(https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/running-your-own-openvpn-server-150x150.jpg) no-repeat scroll 0% 0%; width: 150px; height: 150px;\"></div><div class=\"relpost-block-single-text\" style=\"font-family: Arial;  font-size: 12px;  color: #333333